'''Manwhore'''
# A man who engages in numerous sexual relationships without any reguard for the emotional value of those relationships.

King of all Manwhores - Sam Newman
Sam Newman prowls from bed to bed sticking his great staff into any unsespecting man. This brings him great pleasure as he eats the shit that comes out. He then proceeds to steal all the shampoo, towels and deoderant as he treats each dwelling as a sleazy motel. Returning into the night, the King gives a shifty smile as he sees a ripe juicy ass...

===Usage Note===
Manwhore is to be distinguished from a gigilo, it is not a man who sells his body for money. Rather, this is a appropriation of the pejorative for women (whore, in this case being synonymous with slut) and making it applicable to a man.


